    <body.content>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Correction:  July 20, 2000, Thursday  A front-page picture caption yesterday about work on the Staples Center in Los Angeles in preparation for the Democratic National Convention misstated the timing of the work shown. It was July 11, not this Tuesday.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="correction_text">
        <p>Correction: July 20, 2000, Thursday</p>
        <p>A front-page picture caption yesterday about work on the Staples Center in Los Angeles in preparation for the Democratic National Convention misstated the timing of the work shown. It was July 11, not this Tuesday.</p>
